Sentencas: The development of cathode with high oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) activity is crucial for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: SrCoO3-delta oxides, a mixed ion-electron conductivity (MIEC), are promising cathode materials.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, pure SrCoO3-delta exhibits a hexagonal or rhombohedral structure with poor electrical properties, limiting its application in IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, high-valence Ce4+ is doped at the A-site of SrCoO3-delta perovskite to improve the phase structural stability and electrochemical activity of SrCoO3-delta.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The findings reveal that Ce4+ doping in small amounts significantly advances the conductivity and ORR activity due to enhanced structural stability.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Among the series of samples, Sr0.95Ce0.05Co3-delta (SCC005) presents the best electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, the addition of Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (GDC) further reduces polarization resistance by about similar to 7 times.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The peak power density of 1.3 W cm(-2) is obtained at 750 degrees C for the SCC05-30%GDC cathode.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that A-site Ce doping is a promising strategy to enhance the ORR activity of SrCoO3-delta oxides.
Titulo: Ce-doped promotes the phase stability and electrochemical performance of SrCoO3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
